# assessment-scoring-flows

## Core Assessment Systems

1. Real Colors Personality Assessment
File: src/components/assessment/ColorAssessment.tsx
Importance Score: 85
- Four-quadrant personality profiling (HEART, ANCHOR, MIND, SPARK)
- Custom weighted scoring matrix across 6 trait categories
- Neutral labeling system (A,B,C,D) to prevent assessment gaming
- Domain-specific metadata per style (needs, strengths, challenges)

2. HYRNA Risk Assessment 
File: src/components/assessment/RiskAssessment.tsx
Importance Score: 90
- Eight-domain risk calculation engine for youth needs assessment
- Custom risk thresholds and domain weights
- Auto-adjustment of program levels based on risk profiles
- Intervention matching based on domain risk scores

3. Quick ISP Assessment
File: src/components/assessment/QuickISPAssessment.tsx
Importance Score: 75
- Rapid service plan generation system
- Treatment team composition tracking
- Risk-based intervention mapping
- Early warning signs detection
- Staff approach recommendations

## Assessment Workflows

1. Placement Assessment Flow
- Initial risk screening
